cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.COMM, cs.SY, cs.DC 

The paper deals with optimization problems related to the physical layer of a broadband multibeam satellite system, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), communication and security (cs.COMM), systems and control (cs.SY), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
